Wordplay;;80;;94;;PG;;Filmmaker Patrick Creadon pays tribute to crossword puzzles and those who love them, and features a profile of The New York Times "puzzle master" Will Shortz. Among the celebrities who swear by the Times puzzle are President Bill Clinton, folk-rock duo Indigo Girls, comic Jon Stewart, baseball player Mike Mussina and filmmaker Ken Burns.;;Documentary;;Patrick Creadon;;2006;;NC;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/wordplay